What type of dolphin is this?
There are 40 known species of dolphins, and they all belong to the family Delphinidae. The most common dolphin species found in the wild are:

The Bottlenose Dolphin: This is the most well-known dolphin species. They can be found in almost all oceans and seas in the world, and are very common in coastal areas. Bottlenose dolphins can grow up to 12 feet long and can weigh up to 1,100 pounds.

The Common Dolphin: This dolphin species is also known as the Atlantic Common Dolphin. They are smaller than Bottlenose Dolphins, growing up to 8 feet long and weighing up to 400 pounds. Common Dolphins are very fast swimmers and can reach speeds of up to 20 miles per hour.

The Pacific Bottlenose Dolphin: This dolphin species is similar to the Bottlenose Dolphin found in the Atlantic. They can grow up to 12 feet long and can weigh up to 1,100 pounds. Pacific Bottlenose Dolphins are commonly found in warmer waters around the Pacific Ocean.

The Spinner Dolphin: This dolphin species is known for its acrobatic "spinning" jumps. They can grow up to 8 feet long and weigh up to 500 pounds. Spinner Dolphins are found in tropical and subtropical waters around the world.

The Risso's Dolphin: This dolphin species can grow up to 10 feet long and can weigh up to 1,200 pounds. Risso's Dolphins are found in all major oceans and seas in the world, and are commonly found in coastal areas.

The Pilot Whale: This dolphin species is actually a member of the beaked whale family, but is commonly mistaken for a dolphin. They can grow up to 20 feet long and can weigh up to 10,000 pounds. Pilot Whales are found in all major oceans and seas in the world, and are known for their close-knit family groups.

These are just a few examples of the dolphin species that exist in the world. Each species has its own unique characteristics and behaviors, but all dolphins are highly intelligent and social animals that are capable of complex communication and problem-solving. Dolphins are also known for their playful behavior and are a favorite among many people.
